  - 2 RGB 5050 LED Strips
  - 433MHz power outlet (Chacon & Zap)
  - 433MHz transmitter
  - 1 IR LED
  - Arduino Ethernet shield or 
  - Wemos D1 Wifi (based on esp8266) or
